{"tid":939129,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨59人退黨　湯家驊：深感惋惜","createTime":"2018-12-13T00:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T03:53:26.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"801bd4643a304f3ee8f8701933efc37da1c26179","tid":939129,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181213/s00001/717fc5ff0d67ff60021126975c355682.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181213%2Fs00001%2F717fc5ff0d67ff60021126975c355682.jpg&h=ea084519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擁有700多名黨員的民主黨，昨有59人宣布退黨。曾是民主派公民黨成員、現為民主思路召集人兼行會成員的湯家驊，亦有在facebook分享報道，留言「民主黨深受重創令人深感惋惜」，又說事件令來屆選舉倍增變數。<br />\n<br />\n退出民主黨的59人，包括李永成、丁仕元、區鎮樺、劉其烽及吳錦雄共5名新界東區議員，為創黨以來最大規模退黨事件。退黨者矛頭指向民主黨新東立法會議員林卓廷，批評他「卑劣人格」、「毫無政治道德可言」，並明言會積極考慮組成新聯盟，有消息指會朝劍指2020年立法會選舉方向討論新組織。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷回應時強調，退黨者指控嚴重失實，引述有人認為事件是對他故意「人格謀殺」，但他仍會堅決為港人服務。"},{"pid":"100f5d6ab93b87a8375d3f9406ae6b98751761f8","tid":939129,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:47:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20181213/s00001/1544660764765/民主黨59人退黨-湯家驊-深感惋惜\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20181213%2Fs00001%2F1544660764765%2F%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A859%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%80%E9%BB%A8-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A-%E6%B7%B1%E6%84%9F%E6%83%8B%E6%83%9C&d=hc3C8GZ198Ygz40kVha4nZzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=0d39b99d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20181213%2Fs00001%2F1544660764765%2F%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A859%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%80%E9%BB%A8-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A-%E6%B7%B1%E6%84%9F%E6%83%8B%E6%83%9C&h=2bd5842f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20181213/s00001/1544660764765/民主黨59人退黨-湯家驊-深感惋惜</a>"},{"pid":"3c51be0f3673876977b945e95d9b9